                <p>LUX SEARCH LTD ("we," "us," "our," or the "Company") operates as a specialized recruitment consultancy connecting professionals with employers across Europe. We are committed to protecting your personal data and respecting your privacy rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (EU) 2016/679 ("GDPR") and Cyprus Law 125(I)/2018.</p>
                
